1.install node in your system.
	a.sudo apt-get install node.
2.install npm in your system.
	a.sudo apt-get install npm.

1. install react in your system.
commands:
    a.npm install -g create-react-app (-g i.e globally).
2. Create a folder, go inside the folder open in terminal.create a react project by installing react app. 

commands:
    a.npm install create-react-app project_name.
